{"tid":681704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【蘋果照相機】六四遊行　看得見的良心","createTime":"2018-05-28T09:09:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T09:49:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"324e2d468b34ca16f516bb8ec0a87299de5dbd77","tid":681704,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T09:09:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180528/20403846\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180528%2F20403846&d=LJrlrQnCPRTkRTA%2FSLTgpV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=55deb9e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180528%2F20403846&h=8a4e77d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180528/20403846</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月28日 <br />\n<br />\n【蘋果照相機】六四遊行　看得見的良心<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一張照片勝過千言萬語！<br />\n<br />\n攝影師每日以相機拍下千百萬張照片，將一些大家看似熟悉的東西，以用不同的觀點與角度，讓你重新細看。<br />\n<br />\n【蘋果照相機】為大家呈現新聞重要時刻，以細膩照片，分享鏡頭背後的甜酸苦樂。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果攝記fb：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/1OlyZxX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F1OlyZxX&d=LJrlrQnCPRTkRTA%2FSLTgpV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=50b2da7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/1OlyZxX</a>  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n廣州男：守護中國民主最後一站<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n梁家傑轟港府淪北京應聲蟲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n廣州男：守護中國民主最後一站<br />\n<br />\n梁家傑轟港府淪北京應聲蟲<br />\n<br />\n被問結束一黨專政是否違憲　王振民僅稱「老問題」<br />\n<br />\n29年艱辛路企硬平反六四"},{"pid":"820e48e6a8206bde0534ae664e32441a99e7cb4e","tid":681704,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T09:47:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">泛民打手LIKLN<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/28/174751_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net